# AGENT.md - Coding Assistant Guide

> This file provides context for AI coding assistants working with the {{metadata.name}} MCP Server.

## Overview

This is a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that exposes the Blackboard LMS REST API as tools for AI agents. Unlike the language-specific SDKs, this MCP server provides a curated set of high-level tools optimized for agent workflows rather than a 1-to-1 API mapping.

**Version:** {{metadata.version}}
**Runtime:** Python 3.12+
**Framework:** FastMCP

## Installation

```bash
pip install {{metadata.name}}-mcp
```

## Configuration

Set environment variables:

```bash
export BB_DOMAIN=your-institution.blackboard.com
export BB_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id
export BB_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret
```

## Running the Server

### stdio transport (for IDE integrations)

```bash
python -m blackboard_lms_mcp
```

### HTTP transport

```bash
python -m blackboard_lms_mcp --transport http --port 8080
```

